<![CDATA[<font face="Arial, sans-serif">Date</font><p style=""></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Claim__c.Account_Contact_Name__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Claim__c.Account_Address_1__c} {!Claim__c.Account_Address_2__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Claim__c.Account_City__c}, {!Claim__c.Account_State__c} {!Claim__c.Account_Zip__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Re: Claim No&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>{!Claim__c.Name}</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear&nbsp;</span>{!Claim__c.Account_Contact_Name__c}<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">:</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We received your rebuttal letter dated&nbsp;{!Claim__c.Date_Rebuttal_Letter_Received__c}&nbsp;regarding the resolution for disputed charges on your&nbsp;{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}<span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">a</span>ccount.</span><span style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: justify;">The occurrence of fraud, misuse or abuse on our card program is extremely unfortunate and we are sensitive to the potential business and financial hardships it can cause to our customers.</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">In your communication, you are disputing transactions that you consider suspected unauthorized use.</font></span></p><ul style=""><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -24px;">Disputed transactions occurred on one (1) fleet card - card&nbsp;</font><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Abbreviated_Card__c}&nbsp;and one (1) driver identification number (“DIN”) – DIN&nbsp;</span><font style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.DIN__c}</font><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;assigned as “</span><font style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Driver_Name__c}</font><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;">.”</span></font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="text-indent: -24px;">Card&nbsp;</font><font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Abbreviated_Card__c}&nbsp;</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">was terminated by&nbsp;</span><font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">Fraud Department</span></font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Per your suspicion and per the police report you provided, a former<span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">employee and then current</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">employee, who had been given the authority to conduct transactions on the account, perpetrated the abuse.</span></font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">No attempts to guess at the DIN were made prior to the onset of the abuse.&nbsp;<span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">This would indicate that the perpetrator had knowledge of the DIN.</span></font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Disputed transactions totaling $<font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Allowable_Dispute_Dollars__c}</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span>occurred at multiple fueling locations between&nbsp;</span><font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Allowable_Dispute_Start_Date__c}</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Allowable_Dispute_End_Date__c}</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">.</span></font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Disputed transactions totaling $<font style="text-indent: -0.25in;">{!Claim__c.Ticket_Request_Amount__c}</font><span style="text-indent: -0.25in;">&nbsp;occurred inside merchant locations and receipt copies were ordered on your behalf.</span></font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The remaining disputed transactions occurred at an outside payment terminal (“OPT”), the card was swiped and a valid DIN was keyed in the OPT. Therefore there is no available evidence of merchant involvement.</font></li><li style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We understand a police report has been filed and a suspect identified.</font></li></ul><p style=""></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;has a commercial card account using the&nbsp;{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}&nbsp;&nbsp;Card Program. Use of your&nbsp;{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}&nbsp;&nbsp;account is governed at all times by the&nbsp;{!Claim__c.TC_s_Formal_Name__c}</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;(the</span>&nbsp;“Agreement”).&nbsp;&nbsp;The Agreement addresses unauthorized use and associated responsibilities (refer to section 10.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">However,<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;although we do not believe that&nbsp;</span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}</font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;bears</span>&nbsp;any responsibility for the disputed activity and considering the occurrence of driver involvement, we recognize that this matter has been of great concern and are interested in taking some action to mitigate the financial impact to your organization.&nbsp;&nbsp;In recognition of the mutually beneficial relationship we have shared since&nbsp;<span style="background: yellow;">2007</span>, we are willing to extend an offer to cred<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">it&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}’s&nbsp;</span>account in the amount of $<span style="background: yellow;">XXXX.XX</span>&nbsp;(or approximately 50%)<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">.&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}&nbsp;</span><font style="">will be liable for the remaining disputed portion of $</font><span style="background: yellow;">&nbsp;XXXX.XX</span>. This is an offer of goodwill and does not imply, nor shall it be construed as, an acknowledgment of any liability for the abuse that occurred on the account.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">In consideration of the issuan<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">ce of this credit,<span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}&nbsp;agrees to release&nbsp;<font style="">{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}</font></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">. and its affiliates, including the respective officers, employees and agents of WEX Bank a</span>nd its affiliates, from any claims or liabilities resulting from or related to charges incurred on the above referenced account prior to the date of this letter.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If the foregoing is acceptabl<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">e to&nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: start;">{!Claim__c.Account_Name__c}</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">, please have a duly authorized individual execute the attached copy of thi</span>s letter marked “ACKNOWLEDGMENT/ACCEPTANCE COPY” and return that copy to: Fraud Department, WEX Inc., 97 Darling Avenue, South Portland, Maine 04106.&nbsp;&nbsp;Within fifteen (15) days of our receipt of the signed copy, a credit will be applied to the account.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The foregoing offer will expire on&nbsp;<span style="background: yellow;">April 10, 2018</span>&nbsp;at 5pm EDT.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">This letter is an offer of compromise, and is intended as an offer of compromise, within the meaning of Rule 408 of the Federal Rules of Evidence.&nbsp;&nbsp;Furthermore, nothing in this letter is intended to, or shall be deemed to, create or constitute a waiver, modification, or relinquishment b<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">y&nbsp;</span><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.Partner_Formal_Name__c}</font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">. of any claims</span>&nbsp;or defenses it or any of its affiliates has with respect to the charges incurred on the above referenced account, all of which claims or defenses are expressly reserved.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Sincerely,</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Lucida Calligraphy&quot;; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Lucida Calligraphy&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">Fleet Fraud Services</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Lucida Calligraphy&quot;; font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Enclo<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">sure(s):&nbsp;</span></span><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Claim__c.TC_s_Formal_Name__c}</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">, Fleet S</span>ecurity Measures</span></font></p>]]></td>
